eu.fbk.dkm.internal.springles.config

Class SpringlesRepositoryFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.fbk.dkm.internal.springles.config.SpringlesRepositoryFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openrdf.repository.config.RepositoryFactory

    public final class SpringlesRepositoryFactory
extends Object
implements org.openrdf.repository.config.RepositoryFactory
    Sesame repository factory implementation.

    This class acts as a bridge between the mechanism to create repositories based on an RDF configuration in Sesame and the RDF-based creation mechanism of Factory. This class is not intended to be used directly by user, but rather just by Sesame.

    This class is registered in META-INF/services/org.openrdf.repository.config.RepositoryFactory and is activated by Sesame each time a repository of type SpringlesRepository.TYPE must be created. The implementation is such that the RDF configuration is extracted from the supplied configuration data and used to create a SpringlesRepository by delegating to the Factory mechanism.
